    611 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis is the same license as the BSD-4-Clause, but with a copyright notice for\nthe Regents of the University of California. Captures the retroactive deletion\nof the third (advertising) clause of the Original BSD license for BSD-licensed\ncode developed by UC Berkeley and its contributors (see\nftp://ftp.cs.berkeley.edu/pub/4bsd/README.Impt.License.Change)"
